snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard DIVORCED | Hollywood High
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard reached a divorce settlement just one day before their scheduled hearing in court. The couple even settled the domestic violence case that Heard had slapped at Johnny. Buzz is, Depp has agreed to pay $7 million to Heard so she can walk away from the court case and him.
